<h2>
<br/>Orienteering and navigation training</h2>
<p>Another great way to explore the Brecon Beacons countryside is to join an orienteering challenge - finding your way around a course using just a map and compass. Several activity companies organise this. They can also provide training in basic or advanced map reading and navigation.</p></div>
